#: ../../source/Model_input_output.rst:334
msgid ""
"Locational marginal price -- the marginal cost of meeting one extra MWh "
"of demand at each ``(hour, month, year, zone)``. Discounted to NPV; "
"divide by ``var_factor[year, zone]`` to recover undiscounted real-year "
"prices. Sign flipped from the raw dual so positive means \"more expensive"
" to serve more demand\". Skipped (with a warning logged) if the solver "
"does not return duals (e.g. MIP)."
msgstr ""
"节点边际电价——在每个 ``(hour, month, year, zone)`` 多供一兆瓦时需求的边际成本。已折现为 NPV;除以 "
"``var_factor[year, zone]`` 可恢复未折现的实际年度价格。符号已相对原始对偶值翻转,正值意味着 "
"\"满足更多需求更昂贵\"。若求解器未返回对偶值 (如 MIP),会在记录警告后跳过该项。"

